    "# Demand Forecasting Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "## Purpose\n",
    "Generate 28-day demand forecasts for store/product combinations\n",
    "using the Prophet time series library. Forecasts are written back\n",
    "to the Gold layer as a Delta table for consumption by Power BI.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Why Prophet?\n",
    "- Handles weekly and yearly seasonality natively with no manual \n",
    "  feature engineering required\n",
    "- Automatically detects trend changepoints in historical data\n",
    "- Produces interpretable uncertainty intervals (not just a single line)\n",
    "- Output is suitable for business stakeholders — no statistics \n",
    "  background needed to understand the results\n",
    "- Runs inside a Fabric Notebook without any external infrastructure\n",
    "\n",
    "## Output\n",
    "Table: Tables/gold_forecast\n",
    "Columns: ds (date), store_nbr, product_family, \n",
    "         yhat (forecast), yhat_lower, yhat_upper"
   ]
  },
